Escudo slips on mark , following European trend . The escudo slipped against the mark in early trade on Wednesday , following the trend elsewhere in Europe , traders said . The currency was trading at 101 . 00 / 02 marks , compared with its close on Tuesday at 100 . 88 / 91 , and traders expected it to move in a range between 100 . 91 and 101 . 10 on Wednesday . " The escudo is weaker largely due to the fall of other European currencies ( against the mark ) . But it should not go beyond 101 . 05 or 101 . 10 , " said one trader . German Finance Minister Theo Waigel said on Tuesday that the mark was too weak against the dollar . - - Lisbon bureau 3511 - 3113121 
